@opencatbox
@category{Package grobner}
@closecatbox

@end deffn

@deffn {Function} poly_ideal_polysaturation (@mvar{polylist}, @mvar{polylistlist}, @mvar{varlist})
@mvar{polylistlist} is a list of n list of polynomials @code{[polylist1,...,polylistn]}.
